    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/48c60884cecddc0cd5fec36824101158.avif?t=1761998071\" width=618 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.poster.avif?t=1761998071\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.webm?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.mp4?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏厅仍然流行的那个时代，《Stratogun》肯定会是让你忍不住把所有零花钱投进去的那台游戏机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将体验到80年代最经典的太空射击游戏的现代复刻。快速、硬核、残酷，让人忍不住再来一局。存活的每一秒都必须射击、闪避、反击，在敌潮中挣扎求生；解锁新战舰、武器与特技，冲击全球排行榜。在游戏结束之前，你究竟能撑多久？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/2f305b189fb031b01e048033e0be8bc0.avif?t=1761998071\" width=618 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Stratogun》里的生与死往往只在一瞬间，不断地瞄准和射击是你唯一的求生手段，想要活下去就必须在混乱中前进。将得分转化为经验和新武器，为了更强大的战舰和技能而一直战斗下去吧。致命的红色轨道永不停歇，当屏幕被火光与噪声湮没之时——记住，遵循求生的本能，活下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/20d6f4d7db7009a0185cda03e88b7171.poster.avif?t=1761998071\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/20d6f4d7db7009a0185cda03e88b7171.webm?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/20d6f4d7db7009a0185cda03e88b7171.mp4?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 线框风画面与华丽震撼的视觉特效，加上强劲的电音风复古配乐，你会再次感受到经典街机游戏的真正灵魂。如果你还在怀念街机时代，那么现在就打开游戏，赢下这局。《Stratogun》的战斗不再需要投币，强者只用实力说话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/20f6e4fd1070a8d9b4a37ef448472b14.avif?t=1761998071\" width=618 height=69 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纯粹的街机玩法与硬核难度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战舰、武器、特技培养进阶系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现代风格融合复古视觉与动感电音配乐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球排行榜 </p></li></ul>",
